name: TRIP REPORT | Lufthansa CityLine Bombardier CRJ-900 (ECONOMY CLASS) Munich to Rzeszów
description:
My first trip report on Lufthansa! D-ACNO, one of Lufthansa CityLine's many Bombardier CRJ-900s flew me from the airline's second largest hub in Munich, Germany, to Rzeszów, Poland, the largest city in the country's southeast region. I've flown Lufthansa CityLine CRJs a couple times, as you can see in some of my older videos, but this was my first time documenting the experience as well as flying on one of their CRJ-900s. Lufthansa has outfitted their CR9s with the maximum number of seats possible, 90. If you've watched any of my previous trip reports, I'm sure you can guess what I thought of the legroom ;) Enjoy this European trip report! 

Thanks for watching!
